last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 30
last_episode_to_air.overview: The gang successfully obtains the 850 million from Bassem. However, Fathy soon cons them and takes all the money. Naglaa gives up the gang, which leads to Sameh's arrest, but the rest of them manage to flee the country to continue their scams abroad.

name: Multifaceted
overview: Sokkar is a professional swindler who gets outdone by Omar, another swindler. As she enters into a series of conflicts to get her money back from him, she eventually decides to unite with him to carry out bigger defrauding operations.
